OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy although a few
OL,6,Fbright spells possible in the Central
OL,7,FBelt and south. Largely dry but
OL,8,Foccasional rain across Argyll, perhaps
OL,9,Fturning persistent for a time in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCentral Belt and the south
OL,13,Fmainly dry with just a little patchy
OL,14,Frain, although some persistent rain
OL,15,Flikely later in the night. Occasional
OL,16,Frain turning more persistent across
OL,17,FArgyll. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
