OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy and mild with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, this most
OL,7,Fpersistent and occasionally heavy
OL,8,Facross Argyll.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FUnsettled with showers or longer
OL,12,Fspells of rain on Thursday. Chance of
OL,13,Frain at first on Friday, otherwise
OL,14,Fbright with a few showers. Rain
OL,15,Fspreading east on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
